				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Playing damage song in Bazaar = violation of CoC<a name="53143"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 21 04 10:38 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I've seen many bards tell me that EQDiva and its members endorse playing damage songs in the Bazaar to skill-up.  This bothers many of us in the Bazaar, due to the lag it can cause and the pure annoyance factor.  I looked it up on the Customer Service window, only to find that article soe10250 states that this is a violation of the Code of Conduct.
<br />

<br />
Just making sure you guys know about this, so be careful.</span></td>
